{"tid":483158,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(香港未來?) 窮大學生，異見者在中國被列「低端人口」　","createTime":"2017-11-29T00:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T00:53:44.000Z","uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a760be3feaaea08f1fa89eeb7c59958589d9011","tid":483158,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:34:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171125/20225020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171125%2F20225020&d=KrzM3%2B12F8yz3rimzNYpnDM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=5c19a83e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171125%2F20225020&h=c24eecd5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171125/20225020</a><br />\n<br />\n窮大學生　異見者被列低端人口<br />\n<br />\n「低端人口」最早被稱為「低端外地人」，在中國發達城市尤其北京、上海及廣州，低端外地人特別普遍。被視為低端人口的主要是民工，後來是大城市人不做的保母、清潔工人等外來工。<br />\n<br />\n官媒黨媒常見詞<br />\n<br />\n<strong>近年來，還有農村或貧窮家庭出生的大學生，以及被中共剝奪工作權利的異見人士，都被加入低端人口行列。<br />\n<br />\n低端人口尚無學術或官方定義</strong>，最早出現於去年8月人民網一篇報道，當時中國人民大學教授顧寶昌表示，「通過政策將外來人口特別是其中所謂的低端人口清理出去，導致這些地方常住人口出現增長放緩。但對超大城市來說，這不一定有好處，也不可持續。」文章經網絡轉發，令低端人口成中國官媒黨媒常見詞。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，近年來內地各大城市均出現大城市病，政府出手最痛快的就是清理外地人，並堂皇稱其為「疏解人口」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者廖智廣"},{"pid":"258239078b5170c80cf35bf6f8045e7b9f54259a","tid":483158,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:37:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0440929cfd12750faed4afa7b0cec812e8f1549","tid":483158,"uid":52943,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:40:39.000Z","msg":"不如學納粹德國攪低端人口集中營啦<br />\n一次過送哂入去整人油番皂咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95389d7a0cbdc8a0aa86ba545723071578490148","tid":483158,"uid":13115,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:40:44.000Z","msg":"支蛆"},{"pid":"79035d94efbc81c734f27662c93dcbe43b5d7e0f","tid":483158,"uid":38523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:41:41.000Z","msg":"呢個國家仲有救？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9c3a62bcdd80967a947d2abe4a0495aa9ba966","tid":483158,"uid":41470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:41:43.000Z","msg":"其實係咪得中國先會將自己國民稱為外來人口"},{"pid":"469ccd1d7c31927a4d5bc81f54cbd41d356bad3c","tid":483158,"uid":54593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:51:34.000Z","msg":"香港會唔會有趕走低端人口既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb9e0a5df0f02f9befe4794ab0a5725055d885f","tid":483158,"uid":105598,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:52:28.000Z","msg":"點解香港又要收每日150個低端人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801da1796e1602f1d3a94151008ef0cc2202e5e8","tid":483158,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咪得中國先會將自己國民稱為外來人口</blockquote><br />\n戶籍制就係唔比D人走黎走去"},{"pid":"f0157ffa5ce363d49f787534d10ac929b9a78e15","tid":483158,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:53:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港會唔會有趕走低端人口既一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁窮大學生，港獨派都好可能會變低端人口...."}]}